cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR 

The paper deals with person search, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel end-to-end network architecture that uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on two datasets, which could indicate that it falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
